{"tid":518580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最不快樂地區香港排第7 「希望評分」得10分","createTime":"2018-01-03T13:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T08:35:41.000Z","uid":60207,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb261b92696773b3e8278b32f2d87312e9a6c5f9","tid":518580,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"美國民調中心蓋洛普發表最新的年度調查報告，結果顯示香港在調查的全球55個國家中，不快樂國家或地區排名第7，淨快樂評分僅得29分(滿分100分)，與南非及土耳其同分，而中國、台灣及澳門均榜上無名。<br />\n<br />\n美國民調中心蓋洛普去年底訪問了全球55個國家及地區、5萬多人，調查他們過去一年的快樂指數、對2018年的經濟及整體展望的樂觀程度。「十大最快樂國家」排首位的是斐濟，淨快樂評分高達92分，其次是哥倫比亞（87分）及菲律賓（84分）。排第4至第10位的，分別是墨西哥、越南、哈薩克、巴布亞新畿內亞、印尼、印度，而阿根廷和荷蘭則並列第10位。<br />\n<br />\n而「十大最不快樂國家或地區」首位是連年戰火不斷的伊朗，淨快樂評分僅得5分，第二位是伊拉克（7分）、第三位則是烏克蘭（8分），第四至第十分依次是希臘、摩爾多瓦、巴西、香港、南非、土耳其及加納。香港、南非及土耳其並列第七位，淨快樂評分僅得29分。<br />\n<br />\n調查在香港以網上形式訪問了500人，發現除了不快樂排名位列全球十大外，香港「淨希望評分」亦只有10分，「淨經濟樂觀評分」更是負11分，兩項評分均在全球較後排名。<br />\n<br />\n好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十大不快樂地區 我地係唯一一個有錢但係都唔開心既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9fd65a50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&h=91e935ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888</a>"},{"pid":"7792794061cabaa6aa90a3d2068b1678cf086e9d","tid":518580,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"菲律賓咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b08255d762ddb6a36a8da30dd73c0efe776502","tid":518580,"uid":64175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十大不快樂地區 我地係唯一一個有錢但係都唔開心既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9fd65a50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&h=91e935ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888</a>[/quote]<br />\n貧富懸殊咁撚嚴重都話有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74422e59742fa3354cde92522ddc30dda23f488","tid":518580,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74b08255d762ddb6a36a8da30dd73c0efe776502","tid":518580,"uid":64175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十大不快樂地區 我地係唯一一個有錢但係都唔開心既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9fd65a50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57659888&h=91e935ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57659888</a>[/quote]<br />\n貧富懸殊咁撚嚴重都話有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:58:11.000Z","msg":"相